health_string
Discworld living help
health_string

Name
.SI 5
health_string - String description of health.
.EI

Syntax
.SI 5
string health_string();
.EI

Description
.SP 5 5
This returns a string giveing a string description of how the object
is feeling.  Like Frog is in a bad shape.  That sort of thing.  This
is used in monsters and players long descriptions.

It is a measure of the ratio of hps to max_hps.
.EP

See also
.SP 5 5
query_hp, query_max_hp
.EP
